### ================================================================
### Healthcare Backend — 건강 데이터 개별 조회 API
### REST Client (VS Code) — Huachao Mao 확장 필요
### ================================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

# ① 로그인 후 accessToken 붙여넣기
@accessToken  = YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE
@patientId    = user_001

# ② 조회 기간 설정 (오늘 날짜로 변경)
@from = 2026-07-19T00:00:00+09:00
@to   = 2026-07-19T23:59:59+09:00


### ================================================================
### 1. 심박수 (Heart Rates)
### ================================================================

### 1-1. 최근 10건 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/members/{{patientId}}/health/heart-rates?limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### 1-2. 기간 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/members/{{patientId}}/health/heart-rates?from={{from}}&to={{to}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### 1-3. 기본 조회 (limit 미지정 → 최근 100건)
GET {{baseUrl}}/members/{{patientId}}/health/heart-rates
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###


### ================================================================
### 2. 혈압 (Blood Pressures)
### ================================================================

### 2-1. 최근 10건 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/members/{{patientId}}/health/blood-pressures?limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### 2-2. 기간 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/members/{{patientId}}/health/blood-pressures?from={{from}}&to={{to}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###


### ================================================================
### 3. 혈당 (Glucose)
### ================================================================

### 3-1. 최근 10건 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/members/{{patientId}}/health/glucose?limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### 3-2. 기간 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/members/{{patientId}}/health/glucose?from={{from}}&to={{to}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###


### ================================================================
### 4. 체중 (Weights)
### ================================================================

### 4-1. 최근 10건 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/members/{{patientId}}/health/weights?limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### 4-2. 기간 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/members/{{patientId}}/health/weights?from={{from}}&to={{to}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###


### ================================================================
### 5. 걸음수 (Steps)
### ================================================================

### 5-1. 최근 10건 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/members/{{patientId}}/health/steps?limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### 5-2. 기간 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/members/{{patientId}}/health/steps?from={{from}}&to={{to}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###


### ================================================================
### 6. 권한 오류 케이스
### ================================================================

### 6-1. 환자가 타인 데이터 조회 → 403 예상
# (patient 계정으로 로그인한 상태에서 다른 환자 조회)
GET {{baseUrl}}/members/user_002/health/heart-rates
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### 6-2. 토큰 없이 요청 → 401 예상
GET {{baseUrl}}/members/{{patientId}}/health/heart-rates

###
